'''Electric Love'''<ref>https://www.electriclove.at/en/line-up</ref> is an [[electronic dance music]] festival held annually since 2013.<ref>Magdalena Dorner, Christopher Tafeit, Silke Bruckner  (un)geschriebene Geschichten: Zeitpunkte aus Europa 3738644024  2015 p20  "In ein paar Tagen fahren wir gemeinsam zum „Electric Love“ Festival."</ref> Takes place at the second weekend in July at the [[Salzburgring]] in [[Plainfeld]], [[Austria]]. Headliners have included [[Hardwell]], [[Dimitri Vegas & Like Mike]], [[David Guetta]], [[Martin Garrix]], [[Axwell]], [[Sebastian Ingrosso]], [[Armin van Buuren]], [[Tiësto]] etc. According to ''Technoton Magazin,'' the 2014 festival attracted over 100,000 attendees. It is operated by Revolution Event GmbH.<ref>[http://www.technoton-magazin.com/veranstaltung26_technotonontour_electriclove2014.html ]{{dead link|date=October 2015}}</ref>

According to ''EMF Magazine,'' the festival is "Austria’s leading electronic music festival."<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.emfmag.net/photos/electric-love-festival-salzburg-10-127/ |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140805133559/http://www.emfmag.net/photos/electric-love-festival-salzburg-10-127/ |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2014-08-05 |title=ELECTRIC LOVE FESTIVAL @ Salzburg (10-12/7) &#124; EMF |publisher=Emfmag.net |date= |accessdate=2015-10-17 |df= }}</ref>

